Class OnlineNormalDistributionAnomalyClassifier

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, IFixedClassifier<double[]>, ITaggedEntity

    public class OnlineNormalDistributionAnomalyClassifier
extends FixedAnomalyDetectorClassifier
implements IFixedClassifier<double[]>
    Extends the super class to make use of it as an online learning classifier. Training of the model is done during a warm up time during calls to AbstractFixedFeatureExtractingClassifier.classify(org.eng.aisp.IDataWindow). Until the warm up number of samples have been classified, AbstractFixedFeatureExtractingClassifier.classify(org.eng.aisp.IDataWindow) will always generate "normal" classifications. After warmup, anomalies can be generated if they exceed a threshold from the single mean for each feature element, as defined by the stddev multiplier.
    Author:
    DavidWood
